response.original_title: Beethoven’s Ninth Symphony for the World
response.overview: “Beethoven’s Ninth” is a music documentary on the occasion of the 250th birthday of Ludwig van Beethoven. To this day, Beethoven’s Ninth Symphony is one of the most popular pieces of classical music around the world. In this 90-minute film, you will discover new interpretations of the famous Ninth, performed by passionate musicians.
response.title: Beethoven’s Ninth Symphony for the World
